txt.en: The hendrevail have taken to nesting in Kamskut, a sinister-looking structure nestled in the mountains north-east of Othrikar.

The hendrevail have taken to nesting in Kamskut, a sinister-looking structure nestled in the mountains north-east of Othrikar.\n\nYou should investigate Kamskut, for this nesting behaviour is surely not natural.
Falconer Brúni is at Kamskut in the North Downs, north-east of Othrikar.\n\nYou should defeat Brúni and his falconers.
You have defeated Brúni, a Dourhand falconer, and his fellows at Kamskut.

'You did a great thing for us, ridding us of that falconer!'
'Songs will be sung of your valiant deeds against the hendrevail at Othrikar!'
